# Secrets — NEVER commit. Credentials live here at runtime.
secrets/
.env

# Local handoff doc (not part of the product) — keep on disk, never commit.
RESUME.md

# Per-deployment agent home (generated by `enclave init`; the template lives in templates/).
# A clone ships an empty home/ (.gitkeep) and the teammate runs `enclave init` to fill it.
home/*
!home/.gitkeep
**/chat-reply.md
**/chat-history.jsonl

